data.description: Home sweet home! This beautiful three-story 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom townhome with two-car garage is ready for you!  An open-concept first floor boasts natural light and stunning hardwood floors that take you from the wide foyer to the spacious kitchen. Kitchen features include granite countertops, 42" cabinets, a large island, and a walk-in pantry.  Open dining room has views to both the kitchen and large living room. Living room fireplace keeps things cozy on chilly nights. Walk upstairs to find a loft that can be whatever you need it to be: office, flex space, game room, or playroom! Next up is the oversized primary suite with tray ceilings, space for a seating area, a desk, or just that extra room to make it feel luxurious. In the ensuite find a double vanity, a separate shower and soaking tub, and of course, what's a primary suite without a walk-in closet?! Also upstairs are two secondary bedrooms and a guest bathroom. We can't forget the spacious finished terrace level which includes an oversized 4th bedroom with full bath, and a rec room. At just over two years old, this home is like new! Sweetwater Landing is a picturesque community with sidewalks that lead to the clubhouse, playground, and pool; all with plenty of parking for guests. Schedule a private showing today!
